{{#section "subject"}}
Password Change Successful
{{/section}}

{{#section "plaintext-body"}}
Hi {{{_person.firstName}}},

The password to your Iris account was recently changed. If you 
requested the change, please ignore this email. If you did not 
request any changes be made, then your account may have been 
compromised.

Please follow these steps to reset your password:
1. Login to Iris
2. Select Forgot Password
3. Follow the on-screen instructions.
{{/section}}

